Class SBMLqualHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.colomoto.logicalmodel.io.sbml.SBMLqualHelper

  • public class SBMLqualHelper
extends Object
    Helper to create new SBML documents from scratch or from files using JSBML. It will create a bundle with a convenient access to the document, its enclosed model and the qualitative part of the model.

    Aurelien Naldi
